author: A_Brickset_user
title: Macku
review: Once known as Maku, Macku is the Original Ga-Matoran.She was given out back in 2001 as a Promotion at McDs.She wears the Blue Huna,which is one of Three Primary colored Hunas.On Mata Nui she is Kohlii partners with Hahli,Another Ga-Matoran.

author: Gus_263
title: Not very great
review: The colors looks like the same of hahli, but don't the mask. I don't like the ga-matoran sets 03' very than the other matorans. Macku isn't very playable and have the same kohlii stick and ball. Looks like very the others, 4/5.
